milestones.description: Stuart and Chigumbura's 114-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 103 between Kevin Curran and Dave Houghton
Habibul Bashar has become the top scorer for BAN in ODIs with 1703 runs, going past Khaled Mashud's 1671
